      • EntityBatchLoaderArrayParam

        public EntityBatchLoaderArrayParam​(int domainBatchSize,
                                   EntityMappingType entityDescriptor,
                                   SessionFactoryImplementor sessionFactory)
        Instantiates the loader
        Parameters:
        domainBatchSize - The number of domain model parts (up to)
        Implementation Note:
        We delay initializing the internal SQL AST state until first use. Creating the SQL AST internally relies on the entity's EntityIdentifierMapping. However, we do create the static batch-loader for the entity in the persister constructor and EntityIdentifierMapping is not available at that time. On first use, we know we have it available
